[|] r += n
[|] [`X&]
[|]
{ difference_type m = n; [br]
  if (m >= 0) [br]
    while (m--) [br]
      ++r; [br]
  else [br]
    while (m++) [br]
      --r; [br]
  return r; }
[|]
[-]
[|] a + n [br] n + a
[|] [`X]
[|]
{ X tmp = a; [br]
  return tmp += n; }
[|] [:en] [`a + n == n + a].
    [:zh_CN] [`a + n == n + a]。
[-]
[|] r -= n
[|] [`X&]
[|] return r += -n;
[|] [para:requires]
    [:en] the absolute value of [`n] is in the range of representable values of
    [`difference_type].
    [:zh_CN] [`n] 的绝对值处于 [`difference_type] 的可表示的值的范围之中。
